    [
     {
      "t": "strong",
      "text": "Optional but instructive:"
     },
     {
      "t": "text",
      "text": " measure the voltage across the resistor, then across the LED. They should add up to roughly the 3 V of the battery. This is Kirchhoff's Voltage Law in action — a preview of Chapter 1.2."
     }
    ]
