      "t": "text",
      "text": " and two derived forms. Four quantities tied by two equations leave only two degrees of freedom: fix any two, and the other two are determined. The calculator below is that algebra turned into a lookup — pick any two, enter their values, and read off the remaining two with the formula used shown under each result."
