      "t": "text",
      "text": "A 47 µF capacitor is charged to 400 V across a high-voltage power supply. A 470 kΩ bleeder resistor is wired across it. After the supply is switched off, roughly how long should you wait before considering the capacitor safe to touch (assuming the bleeder is intact)?"
